{"tid":740928,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"志偉幫ViuTV帶隊睇世盃　汪明荃拒影合照","createTime":"2018-07-13T09:11:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-13T09:13:51.000Z","uid":17646,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3c991f948cf518cc6acc4289ab7b34f698b54644","tid":740928,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T09:11:10.000Z","msg":"藝人曾志偉帶領一班藝人現身機場，出發到俄羅斯現場睇世界盃，這次是「ViuTV x 明星足球隊世界盃決賽之旅」，除了明星足球隊之外，現場還有無綫藝人汪明荃、張兆輝和馬海倫，現場他們都沒有貼ViuTV的貼紙，「無綫之寶」汪明荃更避開沒有在ViuTV的Banner及吉祥物旁影大合照，避免尷尬說：「咁唔好啦！」便自行行開。 <br />\n<br />\n有傳志偉跟無綫高層余詠珊不和？他說：「梗係唔會，佢同我、同埋杜之克都係舊同事，係好同事，不過少少嘢已經好多人傳。」有指志偉不滿意港姐有部分是錄影，志偉直認未知是否有份做港姐司儀：「如果有份做，希望多啲參與，我都隔咗一兩年冇做港姐，希望多啲參與。（今年未必有外景？）我都未知，等我返嚟香港，再返TVB睇吓有冇份做先啦！（未來會唔會同ViuTV合作？）未來嘅嘢大家唔知。」另外，志偉亦對無綫解散體育部亦感可惜。 <br />\n<br />\n提到志偉帶隊睇世盃決賽，他透露阿倫（譚詠麟）已帶歌手到當地，他笑說：「阿倫去先嘛！我要拍戲，我哋後面Join。」這次隨ViuTV出發，志偉表示看到網民洗版式留言：「啲網民洗晒版，好多人以為睇錯添，但自己一早應承咗，難得佢咁大手筆，請明星足球隊去，除咗機票，門票都包埋，去當地睇波嘅位都好好，阿倫帶咗好多歌手幫手唱歌，我帶藝人，四年一度，同香港觀眾一齊睇電視，係幾咁高興，係好事嚟！（有冇同TVB講？）OK啦！大家都明白嘅，唔會咁小器，都唔係咁大件事啫。」 <br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180713/photo/bkn-20180713151720515-0713_00862_001_02p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180713%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180713151720515-0713_00862_001_02p.jpg&h=ff427e1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180713/photo/bkn-20180713151720515-0713_00862_001_03p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180713%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180713151720515-0713_00862_001_03p.jpg&h=e8396a5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180713/photo/bkn-20180713151720515-0713_00862_001_04p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180713%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180713151720515-0713_00862_001_04p.jpg&h=8c580797&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180713/photo/bkn-20180713151720515-0713_00862_001_05p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180713%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180713151720515-0713_00862_001_05p.jpg&h=9b2313d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180713/photo/bkn-20180713151720515-0713_00862_001_06p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180713%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180713151720515-0713_00862_001_06p.jpg&h=a2ae2f11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180713/photo/bkn-20180713151720515-0713_00862_001_07p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180713%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180713151720515-0713_00862_001_07p.jpg&h=b5d53b52&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b7252c1042e103585256f6aab27aef12fadd26fc","tid":740928,"uid":146435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T09:13:51.000Z","msg":"馬海倫bb"}]}